The choice of a Bridgerton theme for Lopez’s birthday is also indicative of the cultural impact of the series. Bridgerton, with its lush visuals and elaborate costumes, has reignited interest in regency-era fashion, inspiring designers and fashion enthusiasts alike. Malhotra’s interpretation of this theme, with a uniquely Indian twist, adds a new dimension to the ongoing dialogue between different cultural aesthetics in fashion.
